    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3019"
                            >Robbertus</persName> divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>. Notum fieri volumus universis filiis
                        sancte ac catholicae aecclesiae, quoniam ad salutem et remedium animarum
                        quondam <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosorum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #grandparentOf"
                            ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName> scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf"
                            >avi</rs> ac <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordanis</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs>, nec non <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #parentOf" ref="#people/3010"
                            >secundi Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratris</rs> nostri, ac ob statum nostri principatus,
                            <rs key="#Intercessory">interventu</rs> quoque<persName
                            key="#Intercessory #siblingOf" ref="#people/3022"> Iordanis</persName>
                        carissimi <rs key="#siblingOf">fratris</rs> nostri et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Palatine_count" ref="#people/4262"
                            >Grimoaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Palatine_count">comitis palatii</rs>, in <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Dei et Beati
                            Michahelis archangeli qui dicitur in Formis</orgName>, subdito <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            Montis Casinatis</orgName>, cui domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/4216">Girardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> prehest, per hoc videlicet principale scriptum
                        in perpetuum damus, tradimus, concedimus ac confirmamus <persName
                            key="#Priests #childOf"><name ref="Petrus">Petrum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbyterum</rs> qui est habitator in arce
                            nostra<placeName ref="#places/4550"> S. Agathes</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#childOf #siblingOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannem</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratrem</rs> eius qui est habitator infra <rs
                            key="#Fines">fines</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Fines" ref="#places/4528"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/3028">Sarzani</geogName></placeName>, in loco ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/4557">Pedemonte</placeName>, qui fuerunt <rs
                            key="#childOf">filii</rs> quondam <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Maginardus">Maynardi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbyteri</rs>, cum <rs key="#childOf #heirTo">filiis,
                            filiabus et heredibus eorum</rs> et <rs key="#Public_exactions">cum
                            omnibus hereditatibus et possessionibus illorum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >et cum omnibus terris</rs> quas nos predicto Petro presbytero dedimus
                        et concessimus, praeter <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiarum nostrarum</rs> quas ipse habet. Ita ut amodo
                        et deinceps ipsi omnes predicto monasterio Sancti Michahelis archangeli et
                        domno <persName key="#Prevosts #Personal_rank" ref="#people/4241"
                            >Maynardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs> ceterisque omnibus prepositis et
                        ordinatis ipsius monasteriis faciant perhenniter et persolvat quicquid nobis
                        nostraeque parti publice facere et persolvere debent aut debuerint, et more
                        facere soliti sunt, ad possessionem et potestatem et dominationem ipsius
                        monasterii et memorati domni Maynardi venerabilis prepositi et successorum
                        eius, faciendo exinde quicquid illis placuerit, ad utilitatem et augmentum
                        ipsius monasterii Sancti Angeli. Remota omni contrarietate et molestia
                        nostra et omnium principum successorum nostrorum vel vice principum, comitum
                        vel vice comitum, iudicum sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium
                        mortalium persone. Quod si quis huius nostre dationis, traditionis,
                        concessionis et confirmationis paginam, contemptor aut violator exiterit,
                        aut contra hoc principale scriptum agere presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >quinque libras auri purissimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem predicto
                        monasterio et prenominato domno Maynardo venerabili preposito et
                        successoribus suis, et medietatem nostro palatio. Et soluta paena librarum,
                        haec nostra datio, concessio et confirmatio, firma, munita atque inconcussa
                        maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc scriptum firmius credatur et diligentius ad
                        omnibus observetur, ex nostro sigillo illud sigillari precepimus et manu
                        propria illud corroboravimus. (M) Ex iussione prephate potestatis, scripsi
                        ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3012">Quiriacus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>. In anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo quinto decimo, et nono anno principatus prephati domni <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis Capuae. Datum
                        in <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuano</placeName> palatio,
                        mense augusto, per indictionem octavam. </ab>
